      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride at a great value? This vehicle is a solid choice for anyone seeking a dependable driver! While it shows some character through normal wear and minor cosmetic imperfections, it remains a functional and hardworking car ready for its next owner. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to get behind the wheel of a capable vehicle without the premium price tag!",
