    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless original paint to the pristine interior that still smells like new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a comprehensive service history and no signs of wear or tear. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care. It offers a smooth, powerful driving experience with all features functioning exactly as intended.",
