    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary vehicle preserved in showroom condition. This unit has been meticulously maintained, featuring flawless bodywork and a pristine interior that reflects an uncompromising standard of care. With exhaustive service documentation and mechanical integrity that rivals a new acquisition, this represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector.",
